6. For full development environment (Docker): Run `dev_server/start_dev_server.bat` (Windows) or `dev_server/start_dev_server.sh` (Mac/Linux)

### Stopping the Development Server
1. **Simple Server**: Run `stop.bat` (Windows) or `stop.sh` (Mac/Linux) - stops processes on port 8000
2. **Full Dev Server**: Run `dev_server/stop_dev_server.bat` (Windows) or `dev_server/stop_dev_server.sh` (Mac/Linux) - stops all Docker containers
3. **Alternative**: Press Ctrl+C in the terminal running the server

